BLOCK ACMESystem1Login
ON BLOCK ERROR
    GOTO ErrorHandling
END
    SET Log TO $'''---------------------------------------------------------- ACME System 1 Login'''
    Text.AppendLine Text: Log LineToAppend: $'''Started''' Result=> Log
    Text.AppendLine Text: Log LineToAppend: $'''Launching the ACME System 1 in edge browser''' Result=> Log
    WebAutomation.LaunchEdge.LaunchEdge Url: ACMELoginURL WindowState: WebAutomation.BrowserWindowState.Maximized ClearCache: False ClearCookies: False WaitForPageToLoadTimeout: 60 Timeout: 60 PiPUserDataFolderMode: WebAutomation.PiPUserDataFolderModeEnum.AutomaticProfile BrowserInstance=> Browser
    Text.AppendLine Text: Log LineToAppend: $'''Checking if Fresh login / Session alive for ACME System 1''' Result=> Log
    IF (WebAutomation.IfWebPageContains.WebPageContainsElement BrowserInstance: Browser Control: appmask['ACME Login Page - Browser Edge']['Button \'Login\'']) THEN
        Text.AppendLine Text: Log LineToAppend: $'''Login page loaded - Fresh Login''' Result=> Log
        Text.AppendLine Text: Log LineToAppend: $'''Entering username # %ACMEUsername%''' Result=> Log
        WebAutomation.PopulateTextField.PopulateTextFieldUsePhysicalKeyboard BrowserInstance: Browser Control: appmask['ACME Login Page - Browser Edge']['Input email \'email\''] Text: ACMEUsername Mode: WebAutomation.PopulateTextMode.Replace UnfocusAfterPopulate: True WaitForPageToLoadTimeout: 60
        Text.AppendLine Text: Log LineToAppend: $'''Entering password''' Result=> Log
        WebAutomation.PopulateTextField.PopulateTextFieldUsePhysicalKeyboard BrowserInstance: Browser Control: appmask['ACME Login Page - Browser Edge']['Input password \'password\''] Text: ACMEPassword Mode: WebAutomation.PopulateTextMode.Replace UnfocusAfterPopulate: True WaitForPageToLoadTimeout: 60
        Text.AppendLine Text: Log LineToAppend: $'''Clicking on Login button''' Result=> Log
        WebAutomation.PressButton.PressButton BrowserInstance: Browser Control: appmask['ACME Login Page - Browser Edge']['Button \'Login\''] WaitForPageToLoadTimeout: 60
    END
    Text.AppendLine Text: Log LineToAppend: $'''Session alive for ACME System 1''' Result=> Log
    IF (WebAutomation.IfWebPageContains.WebPageContainsElement BrowserInstance: Browser Control: appmask['ACME HomePage - Browser Edge']['Heading 1 \'Dashboard\'']) THEN
        Text.AppendLine Text: Log LineToAppend: $'''Heading \'Dashboard\' found in ACME System 1 - Session alive''' Result=> Log
        GOTO 'End'
    END
    Text.AppendLine Text: Log LineToAppend: $'''Checking if \'Invalid Credentials\' message appeared''' Result=> Log
    IF (WebAutomation.IfWebPageContains.WebPageContainsElement BrowserInstance: Browser Control: appmask['ACME Login Page - Browser Edge']['Invalid Creds']) THEN
        WebAutomation.TakeScreenshot.TakeScreenshotSaveToFile BrowserInstance: Browser File: $'''%ScreenshotsFolder%\\ACMELoginException.png''' FileFormat: WebAutomation.FileFormat.Png
        SET ExceptionScreenshot TO $'''%ScreenshotsFolder%\\ACMELoginException.png'''
        SET SystemExceptionMessage TO $'''Invalid ACME credentials provided.'''
        GOTO 'End'
    END
    Text.AppendLine Text: Log LineToAppend: $'''ACME login screen / Homepage not found''' Result=> Log
    WebAutomation.TakeScreenshot.TakeScreenshotSaveToFile BrowserInstance: Browser File: $'''%ScreenshotsFolder%\\ACMELoginException.png''' FileFormat: WebAutomation.FileFormat.Png
    SET ExceptionScreenshot TO $'''%ScreenshotsFolder%\\ACMELoginException.png'''
    SET SystemExceptionMessage TO $'''ACME Login screen / Homepage is not loaded.'''
    LABEL 'End'
    Text.AppendLine Text: Log LineToAppend: $'''Completed''' Result=> Log
    File.WriteText File: LogFilePath TextToWrite: Log AppendNewLine: True IfFileExists: File.IfFileExists.Append Encoding: File.FileEncoding.Unicode
END
LABEL ErrorHandling
ERROR => LastError Reset: True
IF LastError <> $'''No Error''' THEN
    SET SystemExceptionMessage TO $'''Error Sub Flow Name : %LastError.SubflowName%
Error Action index : %LastError.ActionIndex%
Error Actio Name : %LastError.ActionName%
Error Location : %LastError.Location%
Error Message : %LastError.Message%
Error Details : %LastError.ErrorDetails%'''
END
